Package: libraryloader
Title: Loading multiple libraries in single call
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sankalp", "Sonar", , "sonarsankalp@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "NA"))
Description: Package is intended to load a list of libraries that would require installing and loading individually.
    This package provides a convenient function, `required_package`, to manage the installation and loading of multiple packages at once.
